ConceptMapLIVDDescriptionProperty

Defines the properties that are further described to aid in the selection of a LOINC code

This value set includes codes from the following code systems:

  • Include all codes defined in http://hl7.org/fhir/uv/livd/CodeSystem/conceptmap-livd-desc-prop
